C, CDD, EDD processes and ABC., including FCPA. Proactively work with internal and external audit and governance teams to understand key issues and resolution plans over AML/FCC matters. Oversee applicable transaction monitoring process and input into design and use of third party FCC systems. Maintain data privacy and protection framework including privacy impact assessments, governance framework, international storage and transfer of information and privacy incident response. Lead and support implementation of new regulations and internal policies and licensing.?? Advise on new rules, regulations and industry consultations. Promote a strong compliance culture and awareness.?? Qualifications 7+ years of compliance experience, preferably in a global financial regulated??business. Degree qualified \u2013 bar admittance or compliance experience equivalent is preferred.?? Excellent analytical and communication skills. Strong stakeholder engagement skills with the ability to connect and communicate at all levels across an organisation. Ability and capacity to absorb large volumes of information and articulate a solution in a verbal and written format. Ability to work independently to advise and confirm technical requirements with third parties.?? Strong collaborative skills and the ability to work in matrix management and coordinate with peer functions.?? "
